description: This dataset contains the annual number of infant deaths annually, cumulative number of infant deaths, and average annual infant mortality rate with corresponding 95% confidence intervals, by Chicago community area, for the years 2005 – 2009.  See full description at https://data.cityofchicago.org/api/assets/0C5D19A1-F520-4E48-A9AD-F51EFD8EF347.
